data.description: Have you thought about building!! Well this is your chance. This property qualifies for a One Time Construction Loan. Builder has plans in place but Buyer has an option to make some changes, at Builders discretion. This amazing home with 4bedrooms and open layout can be your dream come true plus the feeling of living in the Country but close to town. The lot is located outside of the Garden Valley Subdivision, it backs up GV Subdivision but will not require HOA dues.** With acceptable offer Seller will pay the $5,000 Initial Membership fee to Garden Valley Golf and Resort. Enjoy all the amenities of the golf resort and clubhouse. Located in the award winning Lindale School District. This is a great community nestled right off of I-20 just an hour from Dallas and an hour and a half to Shreveport, LA. 20minutes from Tyler, you will find variety of shopping, dining, colleges and health care options. ** Seller does not guarantee all information, Buyer to verify all information.
